---
/**
 * BUSINESS PURPOSE: Builds trust and credibility for Brazilian Portuguese speakers aged 40-70
 * TECHNICAL PURPOSE: Mobile-first about section with credentials, stats, and training gallery
 * TARGET AUDIENCE: Mature adults in Vila Velha, ES seeking professional fitness guidance
 * CONVERSION IMPACT: Personal story and credentials reduce skepticism, build trust for higher conversions
 * LANGUAGE NOTES: Portuguese content emphasizes local presence and age specialization
 */
---

<!-- About Section -->
